  "body": "\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Casio’s 2025 lineup proved once again why the brand dominates across <strong>digital, analog, rugged, and mechanical watches</strong>. From Casio’s first automatic Edifice watch to next-gen G-Shocks and everyday digital classics, this guide helps you <strong>compare, choose, and buy</strong> the right Casio watch for your lifestyle.</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Best Automatic Casio Watch (Mechanical Category)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Casio Edifice EFK-100 Series (Automatic)</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.casio.com/content/dam/casio/product-info/locales/us/en/timepiece/product/watch/E/EF/efk/efk-100cd-1a/assets/EFK-100CD-1A.png.transform/main-visual-sp/image.png\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://monochrome-watches.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/First-Automatic-Casio-Watch-Casio-Edifice-EFK-100-Automatic-Collection-Affordable-Mechanical-9.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">2025 marked a milestone for Casio with the launch of its <strong>first automatic mechanical watch</strong> under the Edifice line. The EFK-100 series blends traditional watchmaking with Casio’s sporty DNA.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Why it stands out</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Automatic mechanical movement</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sapphire crystal</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Premium Edifice styling</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ideal for office, formal, and daily wear</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Buy on Amazon (Affiliate):</strong><br>👉 <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+edifice+automatic+efk+100&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+edifice+automatic+efk+100&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Best Rugged Everyday Watch</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Casio G-Shock Square (5600 / GW-BX5600 Series)</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/7woAAOSwWAFh3I7K/s-l400.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.g-central.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/G-SHOCK-GW-BX5600-IN-HAND.webp\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://nemoknivesreview.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/gshock-premium-square-01206-1.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The iconic square G-Shock remains one of the most reliable watches ever made. In 2025, newer versions improved display clarity and power efficiency without losing toughness.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Why it stands out</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Legendary shock resistance</li>\n\n\n\n<li>200m water resistance</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Solar charging &amp; radio sync (select models)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Perfect for daily rugged use</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Buy on Amazon (Affiliate):</strong><br>👉 <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+g+shock+5600&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+g+shock+5600&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Best Value Digital Watch</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Casio AE-1700H</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.casio.com/content/dam/casio/product-info/locales/us/en/timepiece/product/watch/A/AE/AE1/ae-1700h-1av/assets/AE-1700H_theme.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.casio.com/content/dam/casio/product-info/locales/us/en/timepiece/product/watch/A/AE/AE1/ae-1700h-1av/assets/AE-1700H-1AV.png.transform/main-visual-sp/image.png\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.casio.com/content/dam/casio/product-info/locales/us/en/timepiece/product/watch/A/AE/AE1/ae-1700h-1a2v/assets/AE-1700H-1A2V.png.transform/main-visual-sp/image.png\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The AE-1700H is a <strong>no-nonsense digital watch</strong> with excellent readability and long battery life. It’s ideal for everyday users who want reliability without complexity.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Why it stands out</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Large digital display</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Dual time &amp; stopwatch</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Approx. 10-year battery life</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Extremely affordable</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Buy on Amazon (Affiliate):</strong><br>👉 <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+ae+1700h&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+ae+1700h&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">🔍 <strong>Casio Watches Comparison Chart (2025)</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Model</th><th>Type</th><th>Battery / Power</th><th>Water Resistance</th><th>Best For</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Edifice EFK-100</strong></td><td>Automatic</td><td>Mechanical</td><td>100m</td><td>Office &amp; collectors</td></tr><tr><td><strong>G-Shock 5600</strong></td><td>Digital</td><td>Solar / Battery</td><td>200m</td><td>Rugged daily use</td></tr><tr><td><strong>AE-1700H</strong></td><td>Digital</td><td>10-Year Battery</td><td>100m</td><td>Budget everyday</td></tr><tr><td><strong>GBA-950</strong></td><td>Hybrid</td><td>Battery</td><td>200m</td><td>Fitness &amp; tracking</td></tr><tr><td><strong>MTG-B4000</strong></td><td>Hybrid Premium</td><td>Solar</td><td>200m</td><td>Luxury durability</td></tr><tr><td><strong>G-Shock Nano</strong></td><td>Digital Mini</td><td>Battery</td><td>200m</td><td>Collectible / gift</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Best Fitness-Focused Casio</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Casio G-Shock GBA-950</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/images/img-759.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.g-central.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/GBA-950.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/images/img-764.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The GBA-950 brings <strong>fitness tracking</strong> into the G-Shock ecosystem without turning into a full smartwatch.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Why it stands out</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Step tracking &amp; calorie estimation</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bluetooth phone syncing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Lightweight, flexible strap</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Tough G-Shock durability</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Buy on Amazon (Affiliate):</strong><br>👉 <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+g+shock+gba+950&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+g+shock+gba+950&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Best Premium Casio Watch</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Casio MTG-B4000 Series</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.casio.com/content/dam/casio/global/watch/g_shock/mt-g/mtg-b4000/MTG-B4000_kv_1080x1080.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/fileadmin/Notebooks/News/_nc4/Casio-G-Shock-MTG-B4000-1A.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The MTG-B4000 represents Casio’s <strong>high-end engineering</strong>, combining metal, carbon fiber, solar charging, and smart connectivity.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Why it stands out</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Premium metal + carbon build</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Solar powered</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bluetooth time sync</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Luxury meets extreme durability</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Buy on Amazon (Affiliate):</strong><br>👉 <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+mtg+b4000&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">https://www.amazon.com/s?k=casio+mtg+b4000&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Most Unique &amp; Giftable Casio</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>G-Shock Nano (DWN-5600)</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.casio.com/content/dam/casio/product-info/locales/us/en/timepiece/product/watch/D/DW/dwn/dwn-5600-9/assets/DWN-5600_feature_1-1.jpg.transform/main-visual-sp/image.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://gshock.casio.com/content/casio/locales/intl/en/brands/gshock/products/g-shock-nano/dwn-5600/_jcr_content/root/responsivegrid/container_copy_copy_/container_2062127584/container/container_1167499770/container_copy/item_1751365133186_c.casiocoreimg.jpeg/1763114712008/feature-1-1-1920x1510.jpeg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/fileadmin/_processed_/b/5/csm_The-G-Shock-Nano-compared-to-the-regular-DW-5600-Image-source-Casio-1_7331ae9d79.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This miniature G-Shock is a fun collectible inspired by the iconic square design—perfect as a gift or novelty piece.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Why it stands out</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Ultra-compact design</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Full G-Shock identity</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Lightweight and collectible</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Buy on Amazon (Affiliate):</strong><br>👉 <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/s?k=g+shock+nano&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">https://www.amazon.com/s?k=g+shock+nano&amp;tag=skymaxx0e-20</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Which Casio Watch Should You Buy?</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Office &amp; Formal Wear:</strong> Edifice EFK-100</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Daily Tough Use:</strong> G-Shock 5600 Series</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Budget Digital:</strong> AE-1700H</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fitness &amp; Activity:</strong> GBA-950</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Luxury &amp; Engineering:</strong> MTG-B4000</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Gift / Collector:</strong> G-Shock Nano</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Final Verdict</strong></h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Casio’s 2025 watch lineup delivers unmatched diversity—from <strong>mechanical elegance</strong> to <strong>unbreakable toughness</strong> and <strong>smart fitness tracking</strong>. No matter your budget or lifestyle, Casio offers a proven, long-lasting solution.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">d.</p>\n"
